1
00:00:00,370 --> 00:00:01,370
(All characters, locations,
organizations, and incidents...)

2
00:00:01,440 --> 00:00:03,510
(in this drama are fictional.)

3
00:00:03,580 --> 00:00:05,280
(This production followed
all guidelines for young actors.)

4
00:00:06,580 --> 00:00:08,310
I took in a pathetic worm like you,

5
00:00:08,910 --> 00:00:10,350
and you have the gall
to want to be my son?

6
00:00:10,850 --> 00:00:12,620
Get out of my sight now.

7
00:00:14,090 --> 00:00:15,090
Father.

8
00:00:15,320 --> 00:00:17,260
What makes you think
I'm your father?

9
00:00:17,790 --> 00:00:20,230
You and I don't share
a single drop of blood.

10
00:00:20,990 --> 00:00:24,200
You're the punk your mother had
with another man!

11
00:00:26,230 --> 00:00:27,500
All this time,

12
00:00:28,030 --> 00:00:30,900
- is that how you've really seen me?
- You didn't know?

13
00:00:31,340 --> 00:00:33,370
You were nothing but my attack dog.

14
00:00:34,470 --> 00:00:36,640
Stop it! That's enough!

15
00:00:36,980 --> 00:00:38,880
A father and son
shouldn't act like this.

16
00:00:38,940 --> 00:00:40,410
He's not my son!

17
00:00:41,180 --> 00:00:42,410
Get him out of here!

18
00:00:44,020 --> 00:00:45,050
Se Hoon!

19
00:00:45,620 --> 00:00:48,490
Se Hoon, he's your father,
so you have to hold back your anger.

20
00:00:49,020 --> 00:00:50,820
I've never had a dad
like him either.

21
00:00:50,820 --> 00:00:51,890
You little punk!

22
00:01:00,430 --> 00:01:01,430
Get out of the way!

23
00:01:14,350 --> 00:01:16,550
Se Hoon, what are you doing?

24
00:01:16,920 --> 00:01:18,950
You're leaving the Kunhyang house?
What happened?

25
00:01:18,980 --> 00:01:20,290
This place is a nightmare factory.

26
00:01:20,690 --> 00:01:22,550
And I've been reduced
to a worm living in it.

27
00:01:22,620 --> 00:01:26,890
- Why? You have the Swiss account.
- The password has been changed.

28
00:01:27,960 --> 00:01:31,030
Jin Tae Seok knows
I accessed the account.

29
00:01:36,470 --> 00:01:39,200
Jin Tae Seok completely
deceived and used me.

30
00:01:39,800 --> 00:01:42,610
Let's get out of here.
I have to escape this misery.

31
00:01:46,080 --> 00:01:47,380
Mother.

32
00:01:51,220 --> 00:01:55,420
Mother, stop him. Are you really
going to let him leave like this?

33
00:01:55,450 --> 00:01:58,820
Se Hoon, you should be the one
to ask your father for forgiveness.

34
00:01:59,560 --> 00:02:02,260
You're the one who should beg
for my forgiveness, Jin Tae Seok.

35
00:02:02,260 --> 00:02:03,860
You killed my mother.

36
00:02:03,930 --> 00:02:04,930
What did you just say?

37
00:02:05,000 --> 00:02:07,200
Is that true? Dad, did you kill
Se Hoon's birth mother?

38
00:02:07,200 --> 00:02:10,740
No, Se Mi. That punk found out
he's not my flesh and blood,

39
00:02:10,800 --> 00:02:13,670
and tried stealing from my account.
Now he's spouting nonsense,

40
00:02:13,740 --> 00:02:15,640
accusing me of killing his mother.

41
00:02:16,410 --> 00:02:19,180
Still, throwing him out like this
is a rash decision.

42
00:02:19,240 --> 00:02:20,580
Stay out of this.

43
00:02:21,410 --> 00:02:24,620
- Honey, Se Hoon is...
- No. I won't let this slide.

44
00:02:24,680 --> 00:02:28,490
- Get out now!
- Live long, Mr. Jin Tae Seok.

45
00:02:28,790 --> 00:02:31,020
- Why, that little...
- Honey!

46
00:02:31,160 --> 00:02:32,260
Se Hoon!

47
00:02:44,400 --> 00:02:47,940
My goodness,
talk about a bolt from the blue.

48
00:02:48,040 --> 00:02:50,710
What, are you showing up
as a package deal now?

49
00:02:51,040 --> 00:02:53,440
Young Chae,
were you kicked out again?

50
00:02:53,440 --> 00:02:55,610
We'll just stay for a few days.

51
00:02:56,050 --> 00:02:58,620
Mom, what am I going to do
about Se Hoon?

52
00:02:58,750 --> 00:03:00,420
His father kicked him out.

53
00:03:01,320 --> 00:03:03,920
- Jin Tae Seok did?
- What on earth happened?

54
00:03:03,990 --> 00:03:05,920
You got Ms. Young Chae kicked out
as well?

55
00:03:05,990 --> 00:03:09,230
I chose to leave with him.
Stop talking nonsense!

56
00:03:09,290 --> 00:03:12,200
Gosh, it's hot in here!
Isn't it freezing outside?

57
00:03:12,260 --> 00:03:15,200
Is the boiler cranked up?
Why is it so hot? It's boiling!

58
00:03:17,840 --> 00:03:19,270
Oh my...

59
00:03:20,510 --> 00:03:22,840
So, you're saying Jin Tae Seok...

60
00:03:22,910 --> 00:03:26,950
treats you like you're worth
less than the dirt under his feet?

61
00:03:28,310 --> 00:03:29,550
That's right.

62
00:03:30,010 --> 00:03:31,420
I can't stand him anymore.

63
00:03:31,850 --> 00:03:33,850
He's the man who murdered my mother.

64
00:03:35,620 --> 00:03:38,590
Look, let's be honest.

65
00:03:38,660 --> 00:03:43,330
Jin Tae Seok's a toothless lion now,
isn't he?

66
00:03:43,430 --> 00:03:46,630
So, instead of getting worked up,
just let him bark all he wants,

67
00:03:46,700 --> 00:03:49,570
and you be the immovable rock.

68
00:03:50,600 --> 00:03:54,810
- Can't you do that?
- He's far from being toothless.

69
00:03:55,710 --> 00:03:56,940
Jin Tae Seok.

70
00:03:57,580 --> 00:04:01,410
His name alone can still turn
the whole country on its head.

71
00:04:01,680 --> 00:04:02,780
You're right about that.

72
00:04:04,120 --> 00:04:08,650
There's no politician or businessman
who hasn't taken his money.

73
00:04:08,720 --> 00:04:13,320
Gosh, if that list ever got out,
they would all be ruined instantly.

74
00:04:13,320 --> 00:04:15,290
It'll take more than
stealing his account and title...

75
00:04:15,530 --> 00:04:18,230
to destroy Jin Tae Seok.

76
00:04:19,100 --> 00:04:20,930
And you knew that and did it anyway?

77
00:04:21,870 --> 00:04:23,670
You fool.

78
00:04:24,340 --> 00:04:25,440
This is so frustrating.

79
00:04:26,670 --> 00:04:29,340
If this can't break Jin Tae Seok,

80
00:04:30,510 --> 00:04:32,410
then I'll have to find another way.

81
00:04:38,620 --> 00:04:41,550
Just because Se Hoon was leaving,
why did you have to follow him out?

82
00:04:41,620 --> 00:04:43,120
Was I supposed to stay
at the Kunhyang house alone?

83
00:04:43,450 --> 00:04:44,890
When they just kicked Se Hoon out?

84
00:04:47,390 --> 00:04:49,230
Do you truly love Se Hoon?

85
00:04:50,530 --> 00:04:52,200
Not at first, but...

86
00:04:55,300 --> 00:04:56,330
Now...

87
00:04:58,500 --> 00:04:59,670
I really do love him.

88
00:04:59,870 --> 00:05:03,110
Even after you found out he isn't
Jin Tae Seok's biological son?

89
00:05:03,710 --> 00:05:07,550
Knowing he can never be chairman,
let alone the heir?

90
00:05:07,810 --> 00:05:10,850
Ha Neul, can't you please just
cut Se Hoon some slack?

91
00:05:12,150 --> 00:05:15,590
Can't you just give the chairmanship
to Se Hoon?

92
00:05:15,650 --> 00:05:16,650
Young Chae.

93
00:05:17,290 --> 00:05:19,390
That's not up to me.

94
00:05:19,460 --> 00:05:21,290
I know you plotted with Cha Jung Won
and Han Hye Ra...

95
00:05:21,490 --> 00:05:23,900
to give my Se Hoon a hard time.

96
00:05:23,960 --> 00:05:26,160
I'm just doing
what needs to be done.

97
00:05:26,930 --> 00:05:30,400
- I'm taking down Jin Tae Seok.
- I don't care about Jin Tae Seok!

98
00:05:31,240 --> 00:05:32,740
Just leave my Se Hoon alone.

99
00:05:48,690 --> 00:05:51,390
Are you really throwing Se Hoon out
just like that?

100
00:05:52,460 --> 00:05:55,030
How dare he touch my Swiss account?

101
00:05:55,730 --> 00:05:57,130
Do you have any idea
what that money is?

102
00:05:57,200 --> 00:06:01,670
Bribes for high-ranking officials,
I'd imagine.

103
00:06:01,830 --> 00:06:02,830
No.

104
00:06:03,100 --> 00:06:06,900
It's a pledge to South Korea,
the country I built.

105
00:06:07,000 --> 00:06:09,040
It's money dedicated
to the good of Kunhyang.

106
00:06:12,740 --> 00:06:16,250
But he coaxed my precious daughter,
Se Mi,

107
00:06:16,310 --> 00:06:19,880
and even changed the password.
That parasite, Jin Se Hoon.

108
00:06:20,750 --> 00:06:24,120
Then you should have played nice
and gotten the new password.

109
00:06:28,490 --> 00:06:30,560
But was it really that idiot?

110
00:06:31,830 --> 00:06:33,900
Maybe it wasn't Se Hoon.

111
00:06:34,430 --> 00:06:35,670
Could it be...

112
00:06:36,300 --> 00:06:37,540
Hye Ra, was it you?

113
00:06:41,170 --> 00:06:43,010
You think I would touch it?

114
00:06:43,570 --> 00:06:44,910
Your Swiss account.

115
00:06:47,110 --> 00:06:48,250
Why would I?

116
00:06:49,010 --> 00:06:51,020
I've already thrown in the towel...

117
00:06:52,380 --> 00:06:55,020
and put my Jung Won's future
in your hands.

118
00:06:57,290 --> 00:07:00,590
This paranoia of yours
is an incurable disease.

119
00:07:03,630 --> 00:07:06,060
I'm sorry. You're hurt, aren't you?

120
00:07:06,260 --> 00:07:08,970
If I can't trust you,
who can I trust?

121
00:07:18,040 --> 00:07:22,280
Can Young Chae and her husband
live here, Grandma?

122
00:07:23,880 --> 00:07:26,220
Grandma says...

123
00:07:26,780 --> 00:07:30,150
that they are filled
with a dark aura.

124
00:07:30,860 --> 00:07:34,890
What? Are Young Chae and Se Hoon
spawn of a dark aura?

125
00:07:34,960 --> 00:07:38,130
Don't tell me
Grandma wants them out.

126
00:07:38,860 --> 00:07:42,330
She says they'll only prosper alone,
just the two of them.

127
00:07:42,770 --> 00:07:43,970
Just the two of them?

128
00:07:46,970 --> 00:07:48,540
You mean me and Chairman Gong?

129
00:07:50,240 --> 00:07:52,580
You never understand anything.

130
00:07:52,580 --> 00:07:54,810
It's your own language,
and you're not even an overseas Korean.

131
00:08:02,290 --> 00:08:04,860
- Get out now.
- Hey, hold on...

132
00:08:05,190 --> 00:08:08,160
Mom!
They say to let sleeping dogs lie.

133
00:08:08,230 --> 00:08:09,430
But you're kicking out
your daughter and son-in-law...

134
00:08:09,430 --> 00:08:10,430
in the middle of the night?

135
00:08:10,430 --> 00:08:13,330
Why are you doing this?
You're going to regret this.

136
00:08:13,400 --> 00:08:16,970
I don't care!
Grandma told me to kick you out!

137
00:08:17,030 --> 00:08:18,400
- Mom!
- Mother!

138
00:08:23,240 --> 00:08:25,280
The air in this house
is finally clearing up.

139
00:08:26,010 --> 00:08:28,750
Dad, I know my brother was wrong,

140
00:08:28,810 --> 00:08:31,380
- but does it have to be like this?
- Se Mi, that man used you as bait.

141
00:08:31,680 --> 00:08:32,680
He is not your brother.

142
00:08:32,680 --> 00:08:35,990
You're fueling Se Hoon's rage.
There's no telling when it'll erupt.

143
00:08:36,090 --> 00:08:38,760
That connection ended the day
I divorced his mother.

144
00:08:39,390 --> 00:08:42,060
Raising him as my supposed heir
was my final act of mercy.

145
00:08:42,460 --> 00:08:45,330
He should've been grateful,
but he stabbed me in the back?

146
00:08:46,330 --> 00:08:47,970
He definitely crossed a line.

147
00:08:48,300 --> 00:08:51,770
From now on, my only blood relatives
are you two, Jung Won and Se Mi.

148
00:08:53,600 --> 00:08:55,540
Jung Won, you've changed my mind.

149
00:08:56,470 --> 00:08:59,510
Perhaps I could groom you
to be my successor.

150
00:09:07,490 --> 00:09:10,050
What about Ha Neul?
He's the chairman now.

151
00:09:10,190 --> 00:09:13,890
He's just a placeholder
until Jung Won is ready.

152
00:09:14,290 --> 00:09:15,960
That's too cruel to Ha Neul.

153
00:09:16,430 --> 00:09:17,800
It's your father's decision.

154
00:09:18,330 --> 00:09:20,000
You need to respect it, Se Mi.

155
00:09:20,970 --> 00:09:23,630
You can handle this,
right, Jung Won?

156
00:09:24,540 --> 00:09:28,140
I'll do my best to learn bit by bit,
if I'm given the chance.

157
00:09:28,470 --> 00:09:29,710
I'll be watching.

158
00:09:29,940 --> 00:09:31,080
The four of us,

159
00:09:31,480 --> 00:09:33,080
we're a real family now.

160
00:09:34,280 --> 00:09:38,220
The pure Kunhyang bloodline,
with no impurities.

161
00:09:38,350 --> 00:09:39,350
Understood?

162
00:09:49,930 --> 00:09:53,600
I feel like it's my fault
Se Hoon got kicked out.

163
00:09:54,600 --> 00:09:55,730
It's my fault.

164
00:09:56,100 --> 00:09:57,270
You? Why?

165
00:09:57,670 --> 00:10:00,240
Right now,
this is how we help Se Hoon.

166
00:10:00,770 --> 00:10:02,910
Please make it make sense, Mom.

167
00:10:04,840 --> 00:10:08,550
I'm the one
who has your father's Swiss account.

168
00:10:09,610 --> 00:10:13,250
But I told Se Hoon
and Jung Won the password.

169
00:10:13,320 --> 00:10:16,150
Jung Won, myself,
and Chairman Joo Ha Neul...

170
00:10:16,790 --> 00:10:18,290
joined forces.

171
00:10:18,990 --> 00:10:21,060
Why? What are you trying to do?

172
00:10:21,460 --> 00:10:23,030
Your father, Jin Tae Seok,

173
00:10:24,130 --> 00:10:28,730
will cast out anyone in his way,
even his own flesh and blood.

174
00:10:29,400 --> 00:10:31,840
That's the kind of man he is, sadly.

175
00:10:32,740 --> 00:10:33,840
I know.

176
00:10:35,310 --> 00:10:38,410
I know you were trying to protect me
by not saying anything.

177
00:10:39,410 --> 00:10:40,410
I was.

178
00:10:40,780 --> 00:10:44,850
But as a Kunhyang family member,
you must know and face the truth.

179
00:10:44,980 --> 00:10:48,320
Then why do this to Se Hoon?
Why let him get thrown out?

180
00:10:48,950 --> 00:10:51,690
If Se Hoon gets his hands
on that Swiss account,

181
00:10:52,320 --> 00:10:55,260
he'll take over Kunhyang
and destroy our family.

182
00:10:55,730 --> 00:10:58,760
He could be even more terrifying
than your father,

183
00:10:59,200 --> 00:11:00,770
and do much worse things.

184
00:11:02,100 --> 00:11:04,400
We have to stop him
before he does anything worse.

185
00:11:04,900 --> 00:11:09,810
So that's why you, Jung Won,
and Ha Neul all teamed up?

186
00:11:12,140 --> 00:11:15,680
Then what about Dad planning
to make Jung Won his successor?

187
00:11:16,150 --> 00:11:18,020
He's decided that he needs her,

188
00:11:18,680 --> 00:11:20,720
so it's more about using her
than anything else.

189
00:11:21,150 --> 00:11:22,250
And you?

190
00:11:23,190 --> 00:11:24,420
I want Jung Won...

191
00:11:25,820 --> 00:11:27,490
to grow even stronger.

192
00:11:27,830 --> 00:11:30,430
I want her to become
the true successor to Kunhyang.

193
00:11:30,630 --> 00:11:34,330
So you're getting Dad to trust her,
aren't you?

194
00:11:36,130 --> 00:11:37,900
If Jung Won becomes the chairman,

195
00:11:38,400 --> 00:11:41,770
Dad's crimes will all come to light,
won't they?

196
00:11:43,310 --> 00:11:45,640
As Jung Won makes her way
to the top,

197
00:11:45,880 --> 00:11:49,280
it might look like
she's turning on...

198
00:11:49,950 --> 00:11:52,120
and hurting the people she loves.

199
00:11:52,620 --> 00:11:54,750
Are you sure
you can tell me all this?

200
00:11:56,050 --> 00:11:58,560
Do you want me to help
Jung Won more?

201
00:11:59,460 --> 00:12:01,130
You're an adult now, Se Mi.

202
00:12:01,890 --> 00:12:05,460
You can make
your own judgments and choices.

203
00:12:15,240 --> 00:12:18,010
(Damga Charcoal Grill)

204
00:12:18,080 --> 00:12:19,640
What are you putting in there?

205
00:12:20,410 --> 00:12:23,450
It's nothing. Just getting a gift
for the Kunhyang family.

206
00:12:23,510 --> 00:12:25,280
I can't show up empty-handed, can I?

207
00:12:28,820 --> 00:12:31,190
Hey! Don't touch that!
You'll get the runs!

208
00:12:32,290 --> 00:12:34,020
You put laxatives in it?

209
00:12:34,330 --> 00:12:36,230
I wanted to use poison,
but I held back.

210
00:12:36,960 --> 00:12:38,100
Ms. Jo.

211
00:12:42,630 --> 00:12:46,540
(Vice Chairman Jin Se Hoon)

212
00:12:55,610 --> 00:12:58,350
(Vice Chairman Jin Se Hoon)

213
00:13:05,790 --> 00:13:08,760
- Where did you sleep last night?
- What's it to you?

214
00:13:09,860 --> 00:13:11,200
I'm the son who got thrown away...

215
00:13:11,860 --> 00:13:14,230
by you and Jin Tae Seok.

216
00:13:14,230 --> 00:13:16,170
Since you were about eight,

217
00:13:18,100 --> 00:13:20,140
I was the one who raised you
as my own.

218
00:13:22,140 --> 00:13:23,870
I always worried that
by joining the Kunhyang family,

219
00:13:25,110 --> 00:13:27,010
your own mother
might be cast aside...

220
00:13:27,410 --> 00:13:30,650
and that another woman
had taken her place overnight.

221
00:13:31,550 --> 00:13:33,250
I couldn't stop thinking about you,

222
00:13:33,780 --> 00:13:35,550
worrying that you'd get hurt.

223
00:13:36,920 --> 00:13:40,560
- So I was always on edge.
- I had the same delusion for a bit.

224
00:13:41,630 --> 00:13:43,160
That you cared for me...

225
00:13:43,760 --> 00:13:46,760
more than Jin Tae Seok did.

226
00:13:46,900 --> 00:13:47,970
I did.

227
00:13:48,500 --> 00:13:50,900
No. I still do.

228
00:13:52,000 --> 00:13:55,110
Se Hoon,
you are the son of my heart.

229
00:13:55,170 --> 00:13:56,940
Stop with the lies.

230
00:13:58,110 --> 00:14:00,010
When my son is headed down
the wrong path,

231
00:14:00,910 --> 00:14:03,150
what mother could just coddle him?

232
00:14:04,420 --> 00:14:06,250
Se Hoon, the path you've chosen...

233
00:14:06,820 --> 00:14:09,220
- is already misguided.
- Don't make excuses.

234
00:14:10,250 --> 00:14:11,460
You want to get me out of the way...

235
00:14:12,160 --> 00:14:15,690
to put Cha Jung Won and Joo Ha Neul
at the very top.

236
00:14:16,690 --> 00:14:17,700
Se Hoon.

237
00:14:18,660 --> 00:14:19,830
I want you to come back...

238
00:14:21,270 --> 00:14:24,770
and be the proud and wonderful
my son Se Hoon,

239
00:14:25,440 --> 00:14:26,800
you were before.

240
00:14:26,940 --> 00:14:29,140
I'm not falling
for your sweet talk anymore.

241
00:14:30,440 --> 00:14:32,080
Both Jin Tae Seok and you...

242
00:14:32,740 --> 00:14:35,280
are nothing more than enemies
for me to take down.

243
00:14:35,610 --> 00:14:38,950
- You're not my parents anymore!
- Jin Se Hoon!

244
00:14:44,120 --> 00:14:46,890
Don't make me, or Jung Won...

245
00:14:48,590 --> 00:14:50,130
have to fight you.

246
00:14:51,560 --> 00:14:53,160
Don't turn yourself into an enemy...

247
00:14:54,300 --> 00:14:56,100
that she is forced to defeat.

248
00:14:56,700 --> 00:14:57,870
I'm begging you.

249
00:15:08,650 --> 00:15:12,580
- A nice, simple lunch, wasn't it?
- It was delicious.

250
00:15:12,620 --> 00:15:13,680
That place was amazing!

251
00:15:14,150 --> 00:15:16,320
Don't forget about
the store inspections.

252
00:15:16,390 --> 00:15:20,260
Okay. Let's have some tea,
and then we can talk business.

253
00:15:20,460 --> 00:15:23,730
Team Leader Cha,
you're such a workaholic.

254
00:15:26,030 --> 00:15:28,200
Director, did you have lunch
by yourself?

255
00:15:29,430 --> 00:15:32,140
I haven't had lunch yet.
You should've told me.

256
00:15:32,200 --> 00:15:33,500
I could've joined you.

257
00:15:33,800 --> 00:15:34,940
Young Chae?

258
00:15:35,570 --> 00:15:38,010
- What are you doing here?
- That's Director Joo to you.

259
00:15:38,440 --> 00:15:41,010
- Address me by my proper title.
- Director Joo?

260
00:15:42,350 --> 00:15:43,680
Is she out of her mind?

261
00:15:48,790 --> 00:15:49,790
Young Chae.

262
00:15:52,690 --> 00:15:53,690
I mean, Director Joo.

263
00:15:54,630 --> 00:15:55,930
Yes, Team Leader Cha.

264
00:15:56,890 --> 00:15:58,460
You look tired.

265
00:15:58,960 --> 00:16:01,030
Why don't you head home early today?

266
00:16:01,100 --> 00:16:03,230
How could the Design Team
possibly function without me?

267
00:16:03,500 --> 00:16:06,370
We have to rush the new collection
and prepare for the fashion show...

268
00:16:11,640 --> 00:16:12,640
The fashion show?

269
00:16:13,880 --> 00:16:15,380
(The misdeeds of Plagiarist
Designer Joo Young Chae...)

270
00:16:15,380 --> 00:16:16,850
(have been exposed.
Read the articles.)

271
00:16:19,350 --> 00:16:20,380
No!

272
00:16:21,290 --> 00:16:23,420
This can't be.

273
00:16:27,730 --> 00:16:29,030
Young Chae, are you okay?

274
00:16:30,460 --> 00:16:31,630
Young Chae.

275
00:16:31,630 --> 00:16:34,330
- Call an ambulance!
- Okay, I'm on it.

276
00:16:34,430 --> 00:16:36,170
Young Chae, stay with me!

277
00:16:44,380 --> 00:16:46,440
Is someone dead?
Stop your blubbering!

278
00:16:50,550 --> 00:16:52,880
She's just too fragile for anything.

279
00:16:53,520 --> 00:16:54,750
What's wrong with her?

280
00:16:55,150 --> 00:16:57,550
Is something else wrong with her?

281
00:17:00,060 --> 00:17:01,090
What is it?

282
00:17:01,390 --> 00:17:03,560
Does Young Chae
have some terminal illness?

283
00:17:05,130 --> 00:17:06,430
Young Chae...

284
00:17:08,200 --> 00:17:09,430
is pregnant.

285
00:17:10,370 --> 00:17:11,370
What?

286
00:17:13,570 --> 00:17:14,740
Pregnant?

287
00:17:21,210 --> 00:17:22,710
(Vice Chairman Jin Se Hoon)

288
00:17:29,050 --> 00:17:32,990
(Vice Chairman Jin Se Hoon)

289
00:17:35,330 --> 00:17:37,800
I don't know
what Se Hoon is planning,

290
00:17:38,160 --> 00:17:39,500
but he's like a volcano
about to erupt.

291
00:17:39,900 --> 00:17:41,230
He seems dangerously unstable.

292
00:17:42,170 --> 00:17:46,040
He's waiting to move on Tae Seok.
We don't know his next move.

293
00:17:46,940 --> 00:17:48,410
We have to be ready for anything.

294
00:18:04,320 --> 00:18:05,460
Jin Tae Seok.

295
00:18:06,990 --> 00:18:08,430
Today's the day you die.

296
00:18:09,130 --> 00:18:10,130
Se...

297
00:18:18,970 --> 00:18:20,940
What's that vial?

298
00:18:24,510 --> 00:18:25,780
We're nothing to each other now.

299
00:18:26,480 --> 00:18:28,310
You admitted it yourself,
so why are you here?

300
00:18:36,650 --> 00:18:39,660
I was wrong. I didn't know my place.

301
00:18:40,090 --> 00:18:43,230
- I was out of line with you.
- What's your game?

302
00:18:45,260 --> 00:18:48,930
Se Hoon's asking you to forgive him.
Just let it go, honey.

303
00:18:50,230 --> 00:18:51,340
You changed...

304
00:18:52,070 --> 00:18:54,140
the password to the Swiss account.
Hand it over.

305
00:18:55,040 --> 00:18:56,040
Pardon?

306
00:18:57,370 --> 00:18:59,280
Weren't you the one who changed it?

307
00:18:59,810 --> 00:19:00,810
What?

308
00:19:01,080 --> 00:19:03,610
I admit I found out the password.

309
00:19:04,110 --> 00:19:06,850
When I tried to log in again,
it said the password was incorrect.

310
00:19:08,320 --> 00:19:11,660
- Is that true?
- You don't know it either, Father?

311
00:19:14,260 --> 00:19:15,630
That punk, Se Hoon...

312
00:19:16,330 --> 00:19:18,230
Does he really not know
the password?

313
00:19:19,530 --> 00:19:21,530
The owner of the Swiss account
changed?

314
00:19:22,270 --> 00:19:23,470
Then who could it be?

315
00:19:26,840 --> 00:19:28,310
Se Hoon, that's enough. Get up.

316
00:19:30,870 --> 00:19:32,080
Get up now.

317
00:19:35,680 --> 00:19:37,480
Talk this through with your father.

318
00:19:37,710 --> 00:19:39,020
I'll get you two something to drink.

319
00:19:39,980 --> 00:19:41,320
I'll get it.

320
00:19:41,950 --> 00:19:43,620
I brought some liquor as a gift.

321
00:20:01,670 --> 00:20:03,110
Se Mi, is something wrong?

322
00:20:05,010 --> 00:20:06,280
No, it can't be...

323
00:20:06,610 --> 00:20:08,710
Se Hoon would never do
something like that.

324
00:20:11,450 --> 00:20:14,620
When Se Hoon walked in,
he was holding something.

325
00:20:15,450 --> 00:20:17,450
It looked like some kind of vial.

326
00:20:51,190 --> 00:20:53,190
Farewell, Jin Tae Seok.

327
00:20:55,130 --> 00:20:57,560
Is that poison?

328
00:21:05,000 --> 00:21:08,670
Jin Se Hoon is actually trying
to kill Jin Tae Seok.

329
00:21:14,080 --> 00:21:15,550
Is that for Father?

330
00:21:19,780 --> 00:21:22,550
Do you want me to get some snacks
to go with it?

331
00:21:23,450 --> 00:21:24,450
This is a chance.

332
00:21:24,890 --> 00:21:26,820
A chance to make Jin Tae Seok
trust me even more.

333
00:21:30,330 --> 00:21:33,730
Let Cha Jung Won serve him
the poison with her own hands.

334
00:21:34,630 --> 00:21:35,700
That's not a bad idea.

335
00:21:37,900 --> 00:21:38,900
Go ahead, then.

336
00:21:53,250 --> 00:21:57,290
If Se Hoon didn't change
the Swiss account password,

337
00:21:58,390 --> 00:21:59,620
then who did?

338
00:22:01,730 --> 00:22:03,830
Don't fall for Se Hoon's tricks.

339
00:22:07,100 --> 00:22:08,100
You're right.

340
00:22:08,700 --> 00:22:10,130
It must've been Se Hoon.

341
00:22:11,940 --> 00:22:14,000
Hye Ra,
I don't want to suspect you again.

342
00:22:14,840 --> 00:22:18,310
But why do I feel like
you're lying to me again?

343
00:22:54,540 --> 00:22:56,580
Jung Won. You drink it.

344
00:22:58,480 --> 00:22:59,520
Sorry?

345
00:22:59,520 --> 00:23:03,120
I want to see
whether you see me as your father,

346
00:23:03,720 --> 00:23:06,160
and how far
you're willing to go for Kunhyang.

347
00:23:07,820 --> 00:23:09,060
How can you say something like that?

348
00:23:10,430 --> 00:23:12,460
Are you asking Jung Won
to be your food taster?

349
00:23:13,330 --> 00:23:15,430
Are you saying
Se Hoon really poisoned it?

350
00:23:15,630 --> 00:23:18,070
That's right.
That's what it looks like to me.

351
00:23:20,440 --> 00:23:23,940
Jung Won, drink it. If it's safe,
then I'll drink it. How about it?

352
00:23:24,110 --> 00:23:27,980
- Honey, stop joking around...
- I'm not joking.

353
00:23:44,690 --> 00:23:45,700
See? I'm fine.

354
00:23:53,000 --> 00:23:54,000
Jung Won.

355
00:23:55,940 --> 00:23:56,940
Jung Won!

356
00:24:04,510 --> 00:24:05,720
Where are you going at this hour?

357
00:24:06,120 --> 00:24:08,150
- To my house.
- To Kunhyang house?

358
00:24:08,550 --> 00:24:09,720
But you're not even feeling well.

359
00:24:09,790 --> 00:24:12,520
Se Hoon might be there.
He's not answering his phone.

360
00:24:12,920 --> 00:24:13,920
Something must be wrong.

361
00:24:14,960 --> 00:24:15,960
I'll take you.

362
00:24:25,000 --> 00:24:26,000
What's wrong?

363
00:24:26,870 --> 00:24:29,670
Jung Won drank the poisoned alcohol.

364
00:24:35,710 --> 00:24:36,710
Jung Won.

365
00:24:39,120 --> 00:24:40,480
What happened here?

366
00:24:40,780 --> 00:24:42,090
I'm okay, Ha Neul.

367
00:24:42,490 --> 00:24:43,490
Are you really okay?

368
00:24:44,020 --> 00:24:45,160
They said you were poisoned.

369
00:24:46,420 --> 00:24:47,460
I wasn't poisoned.

370
00:24:47,990 --> 00:24:50,660
Jung Won's quick thinking
saved Jin Tae Seok.

371
00:25:46,750 --> 00:25:48,320
If Se Mi hadn't told me,

372
00:25:49,120 --> 00:25:50,320
I never would have thought to do it.

373
00:25:52,090 --> 00:25:54,590
You should have told me.
Do you know how worried I was?

374
00:25:55,230 --> 00:26:00,000
- I'm sorry.
- I told her not to tell you.

375
00:26:02,470 --> 00:26:05,600
If you'd known, you'd have been
too worried to do anything.

376
00:26:05,740 --> 00:26:07,570
Even so, just tell me from now on.

377
00:26:07,970 --> 00:26:10,640
Anything that has to do with you,
good or bad.

378
00:26:10,640 --> 00:26:11,640
Tell me everything.

379
00:26:12,110 --> 00:26:14,680
Okay. From now on,
I promise I'll tell you.

380
00:26:19,880 --> 00:26:20,980
Where is Se Hoon?

381
00:26:22,290 --> 00:26:23,290
In the annex...

382
00:26:34,230 --> 00:26:35,600
You poisoned the alcohol,
didn't you?

383
00:26:36,170 --> 00:26:37,870
You must have a death wish.

384
00:26:39,300 --> 00:26:40,500
Now you're framing me?

385
00:26:41,100 --> 00:26:42,940
And after I brought you a gift
to apologize.

386
00:26:43,010 --> 00:26:44,980
Jung Won drank poison and collapsed!

387
00:26:45,040 --> 00:26:46,840
Cha Jung Won could be faking it.

388
00:26:47,410 --> 00:26:48,750
I'm telling you,
I didn't know anything!

389
00:26:49,150 --> 00:26:50,210
She's faking it?

390
00:26:50,210 --> 00:26:53,080
I wanted to give you the bottle,

391
00:26:53,620 --> 00:26:55,290
but Cha Jung Won
snatched it from me.

392
00:26:55,790 --> 00:26:57,650
Who's to say
she didn't poison it then?

393
00:26:59,320 --> 00:27:00,890
If you're the one who poisoned it,

394
00:27:02,290 --> 00:27:04,490
you'd better not expect to live.

395
00:27:06,700 --> 00:27:07,930
Dad, stop it!

396
00:27:18,070 --> 00:27:20,340
Should I tell this or not?

397
00:27:20,480 --> 00:27:22,180
Se Mi, you know something,
don't you?

398
00:27:23,980 --> 00:27:26,120
Se Hoon brought the vial of poison.

399
00:27:26,680 --> 00:27:28,320
And I told Jung Won about it.

400
00:27:28,750 --> 00:27:29,750
What?

401
00:27:49,510 --> 00:27:51,440
You found this
inside the Kunhyang house?

402
00:27:51,740 --> 00:27:52,980
We've completed the analysis.

403
00:27:53,780 --> 00:27:55,750
It is poison.

404
00:28:07,060 --> 00:28:09,160
Do you think
Jin Tae Seok will trust me?

405
00:28:10,030 --> 00:28:14,300
He'll believe you're willing
to lay down your life for him.

406
00:28:15,670 --> 00:28:18,700
Even if he officially names Jung Won
as his successor,

407
00:28:19,740 --> 00:28:22,070
will the board of directors
of Kunhyang go along with him?

408
00:28:22,340 --> 00:28:26,040
Jin Tae Seok has a ledger
of his illegal slush fund deals.

409
00:28:27,140 --> 00:28:30,910
It lists the country's key figures
in politics and business.

410
00:28:31,880 --> 00:28:34,550
It's basically a leash
around their necks.

411
00:28:35,050 --> 00:28:37,520
Manager Hwang passed a few of those
on to me.

412
00:28:38,620 --> 00:28:39,620
But that's not all of it.

413
00:28:40,090 --> 00:28:42,160
Jin Tae Seok is the only one
who has the bigger piece.

414
00:28:43,990 --> 00:28:47,430
If that gets out,
it'll throw the country into chaos.

415
00:28:47,930 --> 00:28:49,930
So the source of those funds was...

416
00:28:52,400 --> 00:28:53,600
It's the Swiss account.

417
00:28:54,470 --> 00:28:55,470
It's three trillion won.

418
00:28:59,210 --> 00:29:02,110
Jin Tae Seok will do anything
to find that account.

419
00:29:02,580 --> 00:29:05,680
And the other parties involved
will demand more money.

420
00:29:05,780 --> 00:29:07,750
So they're all monsters
in the same boat.

421
00:29:08,520 --> 00:29:11,090
A network built on
blackmail and collusion.

422
00:29:11,290 --> 00:29:13,660
Then I need to secure
Jin Tae Seok's trust completely...

423
00:29:13,860 --> 00:29:14,860
if I'm to become his successor.

424
00:29:14,990 --> 00:29:18,060
You'll also uncover powerful figures
hiding behind Jin Tae Seok.

425
00:29:18,190 --> 00:29:20,460
If Jung Won is officially named
the successor,

426
00:29:20,830 --> 00:29:24,530
they'll try to get to Jin Tae Seok
through her first.

427
00:29:24,830 --> 00:29:27,840
We have to
make Jin Tae Seok believe...

428
00:29:27,840 --> 00:29:29,570
that Jung Won
is his only viable choice.

429
00:29:40,650 --> 00:29:43,390
I think Se Hoon was the one
who poisoned it.

430
00:29:44,050 --> 00:29:45,290
I wasn't sure at first,

431
00:29:46,260 --> 00:29:48,220
but I knew for sure
when I saw Jung Won collapse.

432
00:29:49,090 --> 00:29:52,330
Even though she suspected
it was poisoned,

433
00:29:52,430 --> 00:29:55,030
she drank it anyway
to save you, Dad.

434
00:29:56,300 --> 00:29:58,740
She drank it, though she suspected
it was poisoned?

435
00:30:02,240 --> 00:30:03,770
So this is what it means
to be my own flesh and blood?

436
00:30:05,180 --> 00:30:08,510
Even knowing you were my daughter,
I tried to kill you so many times.

437
00:30:10,150 --> 00:30:12,680
What is this feeling?
Why does my heart ache like this?

438
00:30:13,580 --> 00:30:15,050
I'm Jin Tae Seok, but why?

439
00:30:16,250 --> 00:30:18,620
I thought my heart was unbreakable.

440
00:30:18,860 --> 00:30:19,860
Why?

441
00:30:23,860 --> 00:30:26,860
(A Graceful Liar)

442
00:30:48,990 --> 00:30:51,190
You are the only successor
I will ever acknowledge.

443
00:30:51,250 --> 00:30:54,060
Vice Chairman Jin Se Hoon,
you are dismissed, effective today.

444
00:30:54,160 --> 00:30:56,660
While my daughter, Jung Won,
trains as my successor,

445
00:30:56,660 --> 00:30:58,760
don't you think you deserve a title
befitting your status?

446
00:30:58,830 --> 00:31:01,130
The slush fund that Han Hye Ra stole
from Jin Tae Seok.

447
00:31:01,130 --> 00:31:02,670
I'm going to take it all for myself.

448
00:31:02,900 --> 00:31:05,500
Sounds to me like the Swiss account
has been compromised.

449
00:31:05,570 --> 00:31:07,600
What's to stop Chairman Joo from
completely dismantling Kunhyang...

450
00:31:07,740 --> 00:31:09,540
after he buys it out
for a rock-bottom price?

451
00:31:09,710 --> 00:31:11,370
There are all these rumors
about you being the successor,

452
00:31:11,610 --> 00:31:12,610
but aren't you just his pawn?

453
00:31:12,610 --> 00:31:15,550
I've realized I'm not Cha Jung Won,
but Jin Jung Won.

454
00:31:15,810 --> 00:31:18,580
I take money,
and I never pay it back.

455
00:31:18,580 --> 00:31:19,850
That's the iron rule.

456
00:31:22,720 --> 00:31:24,720
(Subtitles are provided by KOCOWA.)
